🫧 CarWash Pro
A sleek, end-to-end management and booking platform for professional car detailing.

🚗 Project Overview
This application streamlines the car wash experience for both customers and business owners. Customers can book slots, choose service packages, and track their car’s status, while owners can manage staff and inventory.
  Key Features
Smart Scheduling: Real-time booking with automated time-slot management.

Service Tiers: Support for Basic, Premium, and Full Detailing packages.

Status Tracking: Real-time updates (e.g., "In Queue," "Being Washed," "Ready for Pickup").

Secure Payments: Integrated payment gateway for seamless transactions.

Admin Dashboard: Comprehensive analytics for revenue and customer retention.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: [e.g., React.js / Vue.js / Next.js]

Backend: [e.g., Node.js / Python Django / Go]

Database: [e.g., MongoDB / PostgreSQL]

Styling: [e.g., Tailwind CSS / Material UI]

🚀 Getting Started
Prerequisites
Node.js (v18.0 or higher)

npm or yarn

Installation
Clone the repository

Bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/car-wash-repo.git
Install dependencies

Bash
cd car-wash-repo
npm install
Set up environment variables
Create a .env file and add your credentials:

Code snippet
DATABASE_URL=your_db_url
API_KEY=your_api_key
Run the development server

Bash
npm run dev


